Prerequisites

* Ruby 1.9.2
* Rails 3

Libraries used include

* JQuery
* Haml
* Compass
* Devise
* OmniAuth

To get fully running, you will need to set the following environment variables:

export FACEBOOK_APP_ID=XXXX
export FACEBOOK_APP_SECRET=XXXX
export TWITTER_API_KEY=XXXX
export TWITTER_APP_SECRET=XXXX
export SENDGRID_USERNAME=XXXX
export SENDGRID_PASSWORD=XXXX
export SENDGRID_DOMAIN=XXXX

with the correct values.

Check out http://www.swampcrash.com for working version, as it is